# 1 - organization
# 2 - encapsulation
# 3 - reusability
# 4 - consistency
# 5 - compliance

# what is a terraform module? set of configuration files in a single directory
# minimal module? - LICENSE + README.md + main.tf + variables.tf + outputs.tf

